 Out of the mountain walked a dark figure. Death is his instrument and his 
name. His is cloak flowing by his shoulders. He had been in deep meditation.. 
He had tried to further his skills for the jobs ahead. He locked on to 
Destructor's spark signal and flew off towards the position.
